quran[227]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,"Twâ, sín, mîm."
  26,2,"Oyo nde mikapo mia buku ya polele."
  26,3,"Ozali komitungisa mpo été baboyi kondima."
  26,4,"Soki tolingaki mbele tokitisaki bilembo epai na bango kowuta о likolo, bakingo na bango elingaki kogumbama. (na soni)."
  26,5,"Мре tango nyoso lilendisi ya sika likoyela bango kowuta epai ya Ar-Rahmân, sé bakopesa yango mokongo."
  26,6,"Baboyaki kondima, (na makambo nyoso oyo ewutaki epai ya Nkolo wa bango) kala te bakoyelaka bango basango тропа maye bazalaki kotiola na yango."
  26,7,"Boye bazali kornona mabele te boni tokolisaki kati na yango (milona mibale mibale) na lolenge ya malamu?"
  26,8,"Ya soló, wana ezali elembo. Kasi ebele kati na bango bazali kondima te."
  26,9,"Mpe ya soló, Nkolo wa yo azali wa bokasi atonda ngolu."
  26,10,"Mpe tango Nkolo wayo abengaki Mûssa, kende epai ya bato ya mabe."
  26,11,"Bato ya falo. Bazali kobanga (Allah) te?"
  26,12,"Alobi: Nkolo, ya sólo nazali kobanga ete bandimela ngai te."
  26,13,"Ntolo na ngai ezali ya kokangama, mpe lolemu na ngai elobaka malamu te, tinda yango epai ya Hâruna."
  26,14,"Mpe nazali na mabe oyo nasala bango, na yango nazali kobanga été noki bakoboma ngai."
  26,15,"(Allah ayebisaki ye): Eloko ezali te, bökende bino mibale na bilembo bia biso, tokozala elongo na bino tozali koyoka."
  26,16,"Bökende epai ya falo bino mibale, boyebisa ye ete, Nkolo ya mokili nde atindi biso ya sólo,"
  26,17,"Mpo opesa biso bana ya isalayele."
  26,18,"Falo alobi: Tobokoloki yo te kowuta bolenge?, mpe tovandaki nayo bamibu ebele te?"
  26,19,"Мре osalaki maye osalaki, mpe ozalaki kati ya bapengwi."
  26,20,"Mûssa alobi: Nasalaki yango mpo été nazangaki koyeba."
  26,21,"Yango nakimaki bino тропа bobangi. Sima Nkolo wa ngai apesi ngai bwanya, mpe aponi ngai okati ya batindami."
  26,22,"Wana nde bolamu nayo ozali kokundolela ngai yango, mpe yo osili kozua bana ya isalayele bawumbu nayo?"
  26,23,"(Falo ) alobi; nani Nkolo wa molongo?"
  26,24,"(Mûssa) alobi: Nkolo wa likolo na mabele, na maye manso mazali otei na yango mibale, soki bozali na ntembe te."
  26,25,"Falo alobi na baye bazali pembeni naye ete: Boye bozali koyoka te?"
  26,26,"(Mûssa) alobi; Nkolo wa bino mpe Nkolo ya bato ya kala."
  26,27,"(Falo) alobi: Ya soló motindami oyo batindi ye epai na bino azali ligboma."
  26,28,"(Mûssa) alobi: Nkolo wa moniele na eloli, na manso maye mazali otei na yango mibale. Soki bozali koyeba."
  26,29,"(Falo) alobi: Soki olandi nzambe mosusu otiki ngai, nakokotisa yo na boloko."
  26,30,"(Mûssa) alobi: Ata soki nayeli yo bikamwa ya polele?"
  26,31,"(Falo) alobi: Yaka na yango soki ozali o kati ya balobi bosôló."
  26,32,"(Mûssa) abwaki lingenda lia ye, mpe tala ebongwani nyoka ya polele ebandi kotambola."
  26,33,"Mpe abimisi loboko naye na libenga, mpe tala ekomi pembe makasi pona baye bazali kotala."
  26,34,"(Falo) alobi na bankumu naye bazalaki pembeni naye: Ya soló, oyo nde nganga monene ya boyebi."
  26,35,"Alingi kobimisa bino o mabele na bino na bonganga naye, boye bokosala nini?"
  26,36,"Balobi: Zelisa ye na ndeko wa ye, mpe tinda bato na mboka mpo basangisa (bakende kosangisa banganga, sima baya komekana),"
  26,37,"Mpe bamemela yo banganga ya minene oyo bayebi."
  26,38,"Banganga basangani o mokolo mwa elaka."
  26,39,"Mpe bayebisi na bato ete: Boye bokosangana te?"
  26,40,"Mpo tolanda banganga soki bango balongi?"
  26,41,"Mpe tango banganga bakomi epai ya falo balobi naye été: Boye tozali na lifuta soki tolongi?"
  26,42,"(Falo) alobi: Iyo, ya soló, nakotiya bino pembeni na ngai."
  26,43,"Mûssa ayebisi bango: Bobwaka oyo bolingi kobwaka."
  26,44,"Mpe babwaki basinga na bamangenda na bango, (mpe balobi): Na nguya ya falo ya sólo, tokolonga!"
  26,45,"Mpe Mûssa abwaki lingenda lia ye, mpe tala emeli nyoso oyo basalaki."
  26,46,"Mpe banganga nyoso bakweyaki na kofukama."
  26,47,"Balobi: Tondimi na Nkolo wa molongo,"
  26,48,"Nkolo ya Mûssa na Hânına."
  26,49,"(Falo) alobi: Bondimi naye yambo ete napesa bino ndingisa! Ya sólo, ye nde mokonzi ya bino oyo alakisaki bino bonganga, bokoyeba kala te. Nakokata bino maboko na makolo na lolenge ya bokeseni, mpe nakobaka bino banso na nzete!"
  26,50,"Banganga balobi: Mabe ezali te, pamba te, mpo tokozongaka ya soló epai ya Nkolo wa biso!"
  26,51,"Ya soló, posa na biso ezali ete Nkolo wa biso alimbisa biso, mpo tozali bato ya yambo тропа kondima (ye Allah)."
  26,52,"Mpe toyebisaki na Mûssa ete: Akende na butu elongo na bawumbu na ngai, mpo ya soló bakolanda bino."
  26,53,"Мре falo atindi été basangisa bato ya mboka."
  26,54,"Ete: Ya sólo, bato oyo bazali токе."
  26,55,"Мре ya sólo, balongi biso."
  26,56,"Kasi biso banso tozali na bokebi."
  26,57,"Mpe tobimisaki bango na bilanga mpe mingala."
  26,58,"Bamaziba ya bomengo mpe bisika ya lokumu."
  26,59,"Lolenge moko topesaki bokitani na bana ya isalayele."
  26,60,"Mpe balandaki bango na ntongo makasi."
  26,61,"Mpe tango mapinga mibale bamonani; bato ya Mûssa balobaki été: Ya sólo, biso tosili kozuama (bato ya Mûssa bakanisaki été bakokanga bango ya soló)."
  26,62,"(Mûssa) alobi te. Ya soló Nkolo wa ngai azali elongo na ngai, akokamba ngai."
  26,63,"Mpe topesaki emoniseli epai ya Mûssa ete; beta lingenda lia yo na ebale mpe ekabwani na mibale lokola ngomba ya monene."
  26,64,"Mpe totikaki ete baye wana bapusana. (Falo na bato naye)"
  26,65,"Mpe tolongisaki Mûssa na bato naye banso oyo bazalaki elongo naye,"
  26,66,"Sima, tozindisaki basusu (banguna)."
  26,67,"Ya sólo, wana ezali elembo. Ebele kati na bango bazali kondima te."
  26,68,"Mpe ya sólo, Nkolo wayo azali na bokasi atonda ngolu."
  26,69,"Mpe tángela bango sango ya Ibrâhîm."
  26,70,"Tango alobaki na tata naye mpe bato naye: Nini bozali kobondela?"
  26,71,"Balobaki: Tozali kobondela bikeko, mpe tokokangama sé na yango."
  26,72,"Alobi: Boye bayokaka bino tango bosengaka bango?"
  26,73,"То boye basalisaka bino to mpe banyokoloko bino?"
  26,74,"Balobi: Tokutaki bankoko na biso ya kala bazali sé ndenge wana."
  26,75,"Alobi: Bososoli mpenza тропа oyo bozali kobondela,"
  26,76,"Bino na bankoko na bino ya kala."
  26,77,"Bango banso bazali banguna na ngai, longola sé Nkolo wa molongo."
  26,78,"Oyo akelaki ngai mpe azali kokamba ngai,"
  26,79,"Mpe ye nde aleisaka ngai, mpe amelisaka ngai,"
  26,80,"Mpe tango nabeleke, ye nde abikisaka ngai,"
  26,81,"Mpe ye nde akoboma ngai, sima akosekwisa ngai,"
  26,82,"Mpe nazali kolikia ete alimbisa ngai masumu omokolo mwa suka."
  26,83,"Nkolo! Pesa ngai bwanya (mpe boyebi), mpe tia ngai elongo na bato ya malamu."
  26,84,"Tika ete lolemu na ngai eloba bosoló epai ya basusu."
  26,85,"Mpe tiya ngai nazala okati ya bakitani ya lola ya kitoko."
  26,86,"Mpe limbisa tata wa ngai mpo azalaki 0 kati ya babungi."
  26,87,"Suratu Ach-Chu’arâ Eteni 19 Л 535 \"
  26,88,"Mpe koyokisa ngai nsoni te o mokolo ya lisekwa."
  26,89,"Mokolo moye misolo na bana bakosalisaka te."
  26,90,"Longola sé oyo akoya epai ya Allah na motema ya malamu. (Motema molamu ya kopetoama),"
  26,91,"Bakopusanisaka lola pembeni ya babangi (Allah),"
  26,92,"Mpe bakomonisaka bato mabe moto."
  26,93,"Mpe bakolobelaka bango: Wapi maye bozalaki kobondela,"
  26,94,"Na botiki Allah, boye bazali kosunga bino? To mpe bango moko bazali komisunga?"
  26,95,"Mpe bakobwakama na moto bipai na bipai na bilongi na bango, na baye bapengwisaki bango."
  26,96,"Na basoda banso ya Satana (ibilisa)."
  26,97,"Bakolobaka: Mpe bazali kosuana okati na yango."
  26,98,"Na Allah! Ya soló, tozalaki na libunga ya polele."
  26,99,"Tozalaki kokokisa bino lokola Nkolo ya mokili."
  26,100,"Kasi ezali sé batomboki nde babungisaki biso."
  26,101,"Ata moninga ya soló soló azali te."
  26,102,"Soki tozuaka nzela ya bozongi (ata na mokili), tolingaki kozala okati ya bandimi. (baye bazali kosala bolamu.)"
  26,103,"Ya sólo, wana ezali elembo. Mpe ebele kati na bango bazali kondima te."
  26,104,"Mpe ya sólo, Nkolo wayo azali na bokasi atonda ngolu."
  26,105,"Bato ya Nûh bazangaki kondimela batindami, bazuaki bango bato ya lokuta."
  26,106,"Tango ndeko wa bango Nûh ayebisaki bango: Boye bokobanga (Allah) te?"
  26,107,"Ya sólo, nazali motindami malamu тропа bino."
  26,108,"Bobanga Allah mpe botosa ngai."
  26,109,"Mpe nakosenga bino yango lifuta te, kasi lifuta lia ngai lizali sé epai na Nkolo wa molongo."
  26,110,"Bobanga Allah mpe botosa ngai. İli. Balobaki: Tondimelayo! Kasi"
  26,111,"ezali sé bato bazanga ntina, nde balandaka yo?"
  26,112,"Alobi: Nayebi te maye bazali kosala."
  26,113,"Lifuta na bango etali sé Nkolo wa ngai, soki bozali koyeba."
  26,114,"Nazali oyo abenganaka bandimi te."
  26,115,"Kasi nazali sé mokebisi ya polele."
  26,116,"Balobi: Nûh! Soki otiki te, okozala o kati ya baye tokoboma na mabanga."
  26,117,"Alobi: Oh Nkolo wa ngai! Bato na ngai bazali kondimela ngai te,"
  26,118,"Lakisa bosôló kati kati na ngai na bango, mpe bikisa ngai na baye bazali elongo na ngai kati ya bandimi."
  26,119,"Mpe tolongisaki ye na baye bazalaki elongo naye o kati ya masuwa oyo ezalaki ya kotonda."
  26,120,"Mpe sima tozindisaki baye batikalaki (bapengwi oyo bazangaki bondimi)."
  26,121,"Ya soló, wana ezali elembo. Mpe ebele kati na bango bazalaki kondima te."
  26,122,"Mpe ya solo, Nkolo wayo azali na bokasi atonda ngolu."
  26,123,"Ba aad mpe baboyaki kondimela batindami."
  26,124,"Tango ndeko wa bango Hûd ayebisaki bango: Boye bozali kobanga te?"
  26,125,"Ya soló, nazali motindami malamu epai na bino."
  26,126,"Bobanga Allah mpe botosa ngai."
  26,127,"Mpe nakosenga bino yango lifuta te, kasi lifuta lia ngai litali sé Nkolo wa molongo."
  26,128,"Boye bozali kotonga bikeko na ngomba nyoso тропа kokumisa?"
  26,129,"Mpe bozali kotonga bandako ya minene lokola bokotikala libela awa na mokili?"
  26,130,"Mpe soki bopesi etumbu, bozalaka na mawa te, mpe bobimi bato ya makasi."
  26,131,"Bobanga Allah mpe botosa ngai."
  26,132,"Bobanga oyo azali kopesa bino bolamu, na nyoso oyo boyebi,"
  26,133,"Oyo apesi bino banyama na bana,"
  26,134,"Mpe bilanga na miluka."
  26,135,"Ya sôló, nazali kobangela bino etumbu 0 mokolo mwa suka."
  26,136,"Balobi: Olendisa biso to olendisa te, ezali sé lolenge moko."
  26,137,"Ezali sé ezaleli ya bato ya kala."
  26,138,"Mpe tokozuaka etumbu te."
  26,139,"Baboyaki kondimela ye, mpe tobomaki bango, ya soló wana ezali elembo. Mpe ebele kati na bango bazalaki kondima te."
  26,140,"Mpe ya soló, Nkolo wayo azali na bokasi atonda ngolu."
  26,141,"Ba Thamûd, baboyaki mpe kondimela batindami."
  26,142,"Tango ndeko wa bango Swâlih ayebisaki bango: Boye bozali kobanga (Allah) te?"
  26,143,"Nazali motindami malamu epai na bino."
  26,144,"Bobanga Allah mpe botosa ngai."
  26,145,"Mpe nakosenga bino yango lifuta te, kasi lifuta lia ngai litali sé Nkolo wa molongo."
  26,146,"Boye bokotikalaka na kimiya тропа maye bozali kosala,"
  26,147,"O kati ya bilanga mpe mingala?"
  26,148,"Milona mpe banzete ya nagh’l mpe ya mbuma kitoko,"
  26,149,"Boye bozali kotonga bandako o likolo lia ba ngomba?"
  26,150,"Bobanga Allah mpe botosa ngai."
  26,151,"Kasi botosa makambo ya balekisi ndelo te,"
  26,152,"Baye bazali sé kobebisa o kati ya mabele mpe balingi kobongisa te."
  26,153,"Balobi: Ya soló, ozali sé o kati ya balokami."
  26,154,"Ozali sé moto lokola biso, yaka na elembo soki ozali kati ya balobi bosôló."
  26,155,"Alobi: Nâqah oyo azali na mokolo naye ya komela mayi, bino mpe bozali na mokolo ya komela (kozua) mayi."
  26,156,"Mpe bosala ye mabe te, noki te, etumbu monene ekozua bino mokolo moko boye."
  26,157,"Kasi babomaki ye, mpe na sima bakomaki kolela."
  26,158,"Mpe topesaki bango etumbu, wana ezali elembo kasi ebele na bango bazalaki kondima te."
  26,159,"Mpe Nkolo wayo azali ya sólo na bokasi atonda ngolu."
  26,160,"Bato ya Loth baboyaki mpe kondimela batindami,"
  26,161,"Tango ndeko wa bango Loth ayebisaki bango: Boye bozali kobanga (Allah) te?"
  26,162,"Nazali motindami malamu тропа bino."
  26,163,"Bobanga Allah mpe botosa ngai."
  26,164,"Mpe nakosenga bino yango lifuta te, kasi lifuta lia ngai litali sé Nkolo wa molongo."
  26,165,"Boye bozali kosalela posa ya nzoto bino mibali na mibali o kati na mokili?"
  26,166,"Mpe botiki basi oyo Nkolo wa bino akela тропа bino? Kasi bozali bato ya masumu (balekisi ndelo mpe babuki mibeko)"
  26,167,"Balobi: Eh Loth! Soki otiki te, tokobimisa yo (na mboka)"
  26,168,"Alobi: Ya soló, ngai naboyi maye bozali kosala."
  26,169,"Nkolo, longisa ngai elongo na libota lia ngai тропа maye bazali kosala."
  26,170,"Tolongisaki ye elongo na libota lia ye bango banso,"
  26,171,"Longola sé mobange ya mwasi atikalaki elongo na baye bazuaki etumbu."
  26,172,"Sima, tobomaki basusu baye batikalaki."
  26,173,"Mpe tobetiselaki bango mbula (ya mabanga), mpe mbula nini ya mabe ya motindo wana тропа baye tokebisaki?"
  26,174,"Ya soló, wana ezali elembo, mpe ebele kati na bango bazalaki kondima te."
  26,175,"Mpe Nkolo wayo azali na bokasi atonda ngolu."
  26,176,"Bato ya aîkat, baboyaki kondimela batindami,"
  26,177,"Tango ndeko wa bango Shuaîb ayebisaki bango: Boye bozali kobanga (Allah) te?"
  26,178,"Nazali motindami malamu epai na bino."
  26,179,"Bobanga Allah mpe botosa ngai."
  26,180,"Mpe nakosenga bino yango lifuta te, kasi lifuta lia ngai litali sé Nkolo wa molongo."
  26,181,"Mpe bokokisa bimekelo ya bitando na ndenge esengeli, kasi bozangisa yango te."
  26,182,"Mpe botondisa emekelo na bosembo."
  26,183,"Mpe bobuba bato te na bimekelo na bango, mpe bosala mabe kati na mokili te, (mpe bosomba bosembo ya bato na misolo te)."
  26,184,"Mpe bobanga oyo akeli bino na baye baleka liboso na bino."
  26,185,"Balobi: Ya soló, ozali kati ya balokami."
  26,186,"Mpe ozali sé moto lokola biso, mpe tozali kokanisa ete ozali kati ya babuki lokuta."
  26,187,"Kweisela biso ndambu ya mapata soki ozali koloba bosölo."
  26,188,"Alobi: Nkolo wa ngai ayebi maye manso bozali kosala."
  26,189,"Kasi baboyaki kondimela ye, mpe topesaki bango etumbu o mokolo moye mapata eyindaki, ya solo, yango ezalaki nde mokolo ya etumbu monene."
  26,190,"Wana ezali elembo, mpe ebele kati na bango bazalaki kondima te."
  26,191,"Mpe ya soló, Nkolo wayo azali wa bokasi atonda ngolu."
  26,192,"Ya sólo, yango (kurani) eye, ekitisamaki kowuta epai ya Nkolo wa molongo,"
  26,193,"Molimo mosantu (anzelu gabiliyele) akitaki na yango,"
  26,194,"Na motema nayo mpo ozala okati ya bakebisi,"
  26,195,"Na lokota ya arabo oyo ezali polele."
  26,196,"Mpe yango esilaka kokomama na makomi ya batindami ya kala."
  26,197,"Boye ezalaki elembo te тропа bango, mpo banganga nzambe ya bana ya isalayele bakoka koyeba yango?"
  26,198,"Mpe soki tokitisaki yango epai ya moto oyo azali arabo te,"
  26,199,"Mpe atangela bango yango mbele bandimaki na yango te."
  26,200,"Lolenge wana nde tokitisaki (koyimayima ezala) 0 mitema mia batomboki."
  26,201,"Bakondimaka na yango te kino bakomonaka etumbu ya makasi,"
  26,202,"Ekoyela bango mbalakaka, bakoyebaka te."
  26,203,"Mpe bazali koloba ete: Boye tokozelisama? (mpo tokoka kondima)"
  26,204,"Boye! Etumbu na biso nde bazali kowelisa?"
  26,205,"Boye ozali kornona te, soki topesaki bango mua mibu po basakana,"
  26,206,"Sima maye balakamaki ekomelaki bango."
  26,207,"Esengo eye bazalaki na yango esalisaki bango na eloko te."
  26,208,"Mpe tobomaka mboka te, sé totinda bakebisi liboso."
  26,209,"(Mpona) kokebisa, mpe tozali babubi te."
  26,210,"Mpe ezalaki basatana nde bakiti nayango te (kurani)."
  26,211,"Mpe esengeli na bango te, mpe bazali na makoki ya kosala yango te."
  26,212,"(Kasi) ya soló, bango bamitiye mosika mpona koyoka."
  26,213,"Mpe kobondela nzambe mosusu te elongo na Allah, noki te okozuama 0 kati ya bato ya etumbu."
  26,214,"Mpe kebisa libota nayo ya pene."
  26,215,"Mpe kitisa mapeka nayo (zala malamu) mpona bandimi oyo bazali kolanda yo."
  26,216,"Mpe soki baboyi kotosa yo, loba na bango ete: Ya soló ngai na nazali mosika na maye bozali kosala."
  26,217,"Mpe mipesa epai ya oyo azali na bokasi atonda mawa."
  26,218,"Oyo amonaka yo tango otelemaka,"
  26,219,"Mpe (amonaka) yo tango ogumbamaka."
  26,220,"Ya soló, ye azali moyoki mpe moyebi."
  26,221,"Boye nayebisa bino epai ya nani basatana bazali kokita?"
  26,222,"Bazali kokita epai ya bato ya lokuta basumuki."
  26,223,"Batiyaka matoyi kasi ebele na bango bazali bakosi."
  26,224,"Kasi epai ya bato ya másese (masapo), elandaka bango sé baye babunga."
  26,225,"Boye omoni te ete bazali kolekaleka kati kati ya ba ngomba (mibale?)"
  26,226,"Mpe ya sólo, bango balobaka maye basalaka te,"
  26,227,"Longola sé baye bandimi mpe bazali kosala misala ya malamu, mpe bazali kokumisa Allah mingi, mpe bamisalisi na kopamela mabe ya babubi, kasi babubi bakoyebaka kala mingi te ba nani ekobebela bango."
